'''Karlsberg Bulgaria''' is the [[Bulgaria]]n subsidiary of the [[Carlsberg Group]]. Since 2002, it owns the [[Shumensko Brewery|brewery]] in the city of [[Shumen]], where it brews mainly '''[[Shumensko|Shumensko pivo]]''' (Шуменско пиво).

The company brews two Bulgarian brands – '''[[Shumensko]]''' and '''[[Pirinsko]]''', and 5 licensed brands – [[Tuborg]], [[Carlsberg Beer#Carlsberg|Carlsberg]], [[Holsten]], [[Budweiser Budvar]] and [[Somersby cider]].

